## Quick start

1. Clone this repo
2. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in your credentials
<% if language == "python" %>
3. Install: `uv venv && uv pip install -e .`
4. Run: `.venv/bin/<< project_slug >>-mcp`
<% else %>
3. Install: `npm install`
4. Run: `node src/mcp-server.js`
<% endif %>

