## Configuration

Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and set your credentials:

```bash
cp .env.example .env
# Edit .env with your API credentials
```

## MCP Client Configuration

Add to your MCP client config:

```json
{
  "<< project_slug >>": {
<% if language == "python" %>
    "command": "/path/to/<< project_slug >>/.venv/bin/python",
    "args": ["-m", "<< package_name >>.mcp_server"],
<% else %>
    "command": "node",
    "args": ["/path/to/<< project_slug >>/src/mcp-server.js"],
<% endif %>
    "env": {
      "DOTENV_PATH": "/path/to/<< project_slug >>/.env"
    }
  }
}
```

